OL,3,CNearly two dozen modern slavery cases
OL,4,Cin south Wales last year alone
OL,6,FThere were 19 confirmed cases of
OL,7,Fmodern slavery in last year alone,
OL,8,Faccording to new figures from a
OL,9,Fleading charity.
OL,11,FUnseen said calls to its UK-wide anti-
OL,12,Fslavery helpline reached a record
OL,13,Fhigh, with the number of potential
OL,14,Fvictims in the rising by nearly a
OL,15,Fthird and suspected cases of forced
OL,16,Fsurrogacy being reported for the first
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,19,FThe charity's study also found another
OL,20,F90 potential modern slavery victims in
OL,21,Fsouth Wales last year.
