OL,6,FDemand for Unseen's services - via its
OL,7,Fhelpline, online or via the charity's
OL,8,Fapp - across the UK have risen
OL,9,F"significantly" for the fourth year in
OL,10,Fa row.
OL,12,FThere were 11,700 "contacts" with the
OL,13,Fcharity's helpline for and
OL,14,Fexploitation in 2023, up by nearly a
OL,15,Ffifth compared to 2022.
OL,17,FHowever, Unseen's director Justine
OL,18,FCarter said the increase indicated "we
OL,19,Fare succeeding in raising awareness of
OL,20,Fthe issue and mobilising more people
OL,21,Fto act".
