OL,6,FThe anti-slavery charity's annual
OL,7,Freport shows a 30% rise in potential
OL,8,Fvictims working in the care sector.
OL,9,FIt's an area which has been a
OL,10,F"concern" to the charity "for some
OL,11,Ftime."
OL,13,FMs Carter suggested people could be
OL,14,Fput off reporting concerns due to the
OL,15,Ffear of being deported, with a
OL,16,Fsignificant proportion of victims
OL,17,Fcoming from abroad.
