OL,6,FIn 2023, potential victims came from
OL,7,F106 countries, up from 99 the previous
OL,8,Fyear. This included a higher number of
OL,9,Fpeople from India than from any other
OL,10,Fcountry for the first time.
OL,12,FShe said: "We remain concerned that
OL,13,Fthe ever-increasing hostile
OL,14,Fenvironment in the UK towards migrants
OL,15,Fand foreign workers means that fewer
OL,16,Fpeople feel able to raise concerns and
OL,17,Fseek the help and support that they
OL,18,Fdesperately need.
